<topic xmlns:cba="http://www.dita-semia.org/conbat" id="gh2_vhd_xt">
  <title>Definition List</title>
  <body>
		<p>Predefined definition terms with different output classes.</p>
		<section>
			<title>Standard Layout</title>
			<p>Outputclass: &lt;empty></p>
			<dl>
				<dd cba:dt="Term 1">Description of 1st term.</dd>
				<dd cba:dt="Term 2">Description of 2nd term.</dd>
				<dd cba:dt="Term 3">Description of 3rd term.</dd>
			</dl>
			<p>Reference <codeph>dl</codeph> element without Conbat:</p>
			<dl>
				<dlentry>
					<dt>Term 1</dt>
					<dd>Description of 1st term.</dd>
				</dlentry>
				<dlentry>
					<dt>Term 2</dt>
					<dd>Description of 2nd term.</dd>
				</dlentry>
				<dlentry>
					<dt>Term 3</dt>
					<dd>Description of 3rd term.</dd>
				</dlentry>
			</dl>
		</section>
		<section>
			<title>Bullet List With Titles</title>
			<p>Outputclass: <codeph>bullet-list-titles</codeph></p>
			<dl outputclass="bullet-list-titles">
				<dd cba:dt="Term 1">Description of 1st term.</dd>
				<dd cba:dt="Term 2">Description of 2nd term.</dd>
				<dd cba:dt="Term 3">Description of 3rd term.</dd>
			</dl>
			<p>Reference <codeph>dl</codeph> element without Conbat:</p>
			<dl outputclass="bullet-list-titles">
				<dlentry>
					<dt>Term 1</dt>
					<dd>Description of 1st term.</dd>
				</dlentry>
				<dlentry>
					<dt>Term 2</dt>
					<dd>Description of 2nd term.</dd>
				</dlentry>
				<dlentry>
					<dt>Term 3</dt>
					<dd>Description of 3rd term.</dd>
				</dlentry>
			</dl>
		</section>
		<section id="vk1_hhr_zt">
			<title>Bullet List With Dashes</title>
			<p>Outputclass: <codeph>bullet-list-dashes</codeph></p>
			<dl outputclass="bullet-list-dashes">
				<dd cba:dt="Term 1">Description of 1st term.</dd>
				<dd cba:dt="Term 2">Description of 2nd term.</dd>
				<dd cba:dt="Term 3">Description of 3rd term.</dd>
			</dl>
